<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.5.6">
<l>kiṭantāṉait taṭaṅkaṭaluḷ paṇaṅkaḷ mēvik kiḷarppoṟiya maṟitiriya vataṉiṉ piṉṉē</l>
<l>paṭarntāṉaip paṭumatatta kaḷiṟṟiṉ kompu paṟittāṉaip pāriṭattai yeyiṟu kīṟa</l>
<l>viṭantāṉai vaḷaimaruppi ṉēṉa māki yirunilaṉum peruvicumpu meytā vaṇṇam</l>
<l>kaṭantāṉai yemmāṉaik kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ kaṭipoḻilcūḻ kaṭalmallait talaca yaṉattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who lies in the vast sea abiding on [serpent] hoods,</l>
<l rend="indent">who ran behind a bright, spotted deer as it roamed,</l>
<l>The one who tore off the mad, rutting elephant’s tusk [and] who,</l>
<l rend="indent">as a boar with curved tusks, rooted up the earth’s expanse</l>
<l rend="indent">to extract [it] with [its] teeth,</l>
<l>The one who measured [in such] a way that the vast heaven</l>
<l rend="indent">and wide world were insufficient,</l>
<l>Our lord, I saw for myself in Talacayaṉam encircled by fragrant gardens</l>
<l rend="indent">at Mallai by the sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
